cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with self-supervised learning on videos to learn class-specific image embeddings, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a hierarchical probabilistic network decoder model, which is a machine learning technique (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of embeddings for downstream tasks, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper uses neural networks for learning embeddings, which is a subfield of neural engineering (cs.NE).
